---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>AmicBridge – Private Peer-to-Peer Lending Network</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="AmicBridge is a private, identity-checked peer-to-peer network that connects real borrowers and lenders through structured requests and a trusted bridge."
    />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  </head>

  <body class="page">
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header class="header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
        <div class="logo">
          <span class="logo-mark">A</span>
          <span class="logo-text">AmicBridge</span>
        </div>

        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="#about" class="nav-link">About</a>
          <a href="#how" class="nav-link">How it works</a>
          <a href="#trust" class="nav-link">Trust & identity</a>
          <a href="#borrow" class="nav-link">Borrow</a>
          <a href="#lend" class="nav-link">Lend</a>
          <a href="#strategy" class="nav-link">Strategy</a>
          <a href="#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-inner">
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          A private, trusted bridge between real borrowers and real lenders.
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          AmicBridge is a private peer-to-peer network. Every member goes through
          identity checks before being allowed into the network, and every request
          is collected in a clear, structured way. Our role is to be the trusted
          bridge: we review who is entering, how they present themselves, and how
          they describe what they want to borrow or lend.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-buttons">
          <a href="#borrow" class="btn btn-primary">Request a loan</a>
          <a href="#lend" class="btn btn-secondary">Offer lending</a>
        </div>

        <p class="hero-note">
          AmicBridge never holds funds or crypto, never signs loan contracts, and never
          guarantees repayment, returns or matches. All agreements and transfers happen
          directly between members, who must make their own decisions and assessments.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ABOUT / WHAT IS AMICBRIDGE -->
    <section id="about" class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">What is AmicBridge?</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          AmicBridge is a private network where people who want to borrow and people who
          want to lend can meet in a controlled environment. It is not an open
          marketplace for anyone with a link. Only identity-checked members are allowed
          to participate.
        </p>

        <ul class="bridge-list">
          <li>Private network, not a public bulletin board</li>
          <li>Identity checks on all members before they are allowed in</li>
          <li>Structured forms for borrowing, lending and strategy requests</li>
          <li>No custody of funds, no holding of crypto or bank deposits</li>
          <li>Direct agreements and transfers between members only</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
    <section id="how" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">How the trusted bridge works</h2>
        <div class="how-grid">
          <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-number">1</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Send a request</h3>
              <p>
                You submit a borrowing request, lending offer or strategy request using
                a structured form. Your information is sent privately to AmicBridge for
                review.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-number">2</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Identity check</h3>
              <p>
                Before anyone is allowed into the private network, AmicBridge performs
                identity checks on that member. This confirms who they say they are and
                creates accountability inside the network.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-number">3</span>
            <div>
              <h3>Careful matching & direct contact</h3>
              <p>
                Where there is a suitable fit, AmicBridge can act as the bridge between
                borrower and lender. Members then communicate and decide directly
                between themselves what to do, if anything.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRUST & IDENTITY -->
    <section id="trust" class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Trust & identity checks</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          Trust begins with knowing who is inside the network. AmicBridge is built
          around the idea that private, identity-checked networks are safer and more
          serious than anonymous crowds.
        </p>

        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="principle-card">
            <h3>Private network</h3>
            <p>
              AmicBridge is not open to everyone. Only members who pass identity checks
              and basic review can join the private environment.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle-card">
            <h3>Identity checks on all members</h3>
            <p>
              We perform identity checks on every member before they are allowed in. This
              creates accountability, but it does not mean zero risk or a guarantee of
              repayment.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle-card">
            <h3>Clarity over hype</h3>
            <p>
              Requests use structured fields so borrowers and lenders see clear
              information, not vague promises.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="principle-card">
            <h3>No unrealistic promises</h3>
            <p>
              We do not promise safe returns, guaranteed loans or profits. Our role is
              the bridge, not the outcome.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- BORROW FORM -->
    <section id="borrow" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Send a borrowing request</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          Use this form if you want to borrow. Your request goes privately to AmicBridge.
          If you are not yet a member, we will contact you and complete identity checks
          first before any possible introduction.
        </p>

        <form
          class="form"
          action="https://formspree.io/f/movgnjyd"
          method="POST"
        >
          <input
            type="hidden"
            name="_subject"
            value="New BORROW request on AmicBridge"
          />
          <input type="hidden" name="request_type" value="borrow" />

          <label>
            Full name
            <input type="text" name="full_name" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Email
            <input type="email" name="email" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Country of residence
            <input type="text" name="country" required />
          </label>

          <div class="form-row">
            <label>
              Amount you want to borrow
              <input type="number" name="amount" min="1" required />
            </label>

            <label>
              Asset
              <select name="asset">
                <option>EUR</option>
                <option>USD</option>
                <option>NOK</option>
                <option>BTC</option>
                <option>ETH</option>
                <option>USDT</option>
              </select>
            </label>
          </div>

          <label>
            Desired duration
            <select name="duration">
              <option>Up to 6 months</option>
              <option>Up to 12 months</option>
              <option>Up to 24 months</option>
              <option>Up to 36 months</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <label>
            Max annual interest you can accept
            <input type="number" name="max_interest" min="1" max="40" />
          </label>

          <label>
            Purpose and how you plan to repay
            <textarea name="purpose" rows="3"></textarea>
          </label>

          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Submit borrowing request</button>

          <p class="card-note">
            This form does not create a loan. It is an invitation to begin a review and
            identity process inside the private network. All decisions remain yours.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- LEND FORM -->
    <section id="lend" class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Send a lending offer</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          Use this form if you want to lend. Your offer goes privately to AmicBridge.
          Identity checks are required before you can become a member of the private
          network and be considered as a lender.
        </p>

        <form
          class="form"
          action="https://formspree.io/f/movgnjyd"
          method="POST"
        >
          <input
            type="hidden"
            name="_subject"
            value="New LEND offer on AmicBridge"
          />
          <input type="hidden" name="request_type" value="lend" />

          <label>
            Full name
            <input type="text" name="full_name" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Email
            <input type="email" name="email" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Country of residence
            <input type="text" name="country" required />
          </label>

          <div class="form-row">
            <label>
              Amount you are willing to lend
              <input type="number" name="amount" min="1" required />
            </label>

            <label>
              Asset
              <select name="asset">
                <option>EUR</option>
                <option>USD</option>
                <option>NOK</option>
                <option>BTC</option>
                <option>ETH</option>
                <option>USDT</option>
              </select>
            </label>
          </div>

          <label>
            Target annual interest
            <input type="number" name="target_interest" min="1" max="40" />
          </label>

          <label>
            What kind of borrower are you looking for?
            <textarea name="preferred_borrower" rows="3"></textarea>
          </label>

          <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-full">Submit lending offer</button>

          <p class="card-note">
            Lending is risky. Even inside a private, identity-checked network, borrowers
            may fail to repay. Never lend more than you can afford to lose.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STRATEGY FORM -->
    <section id="strategy" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Request investment strategy ideas</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          Use this form if you want to request investment strategy ideas and guidance.
          Any ideas are for information and education only – not guaranteed results.
        </p>

        <form
          class="form"
          action="https://formspree.io/f/movgnjyd"
          method="POST"
        >
          <input
            type="hidden"
            name="_subject"
            value="New STRATEGY request on AmicBridge"
          />
          <input type="hidden" name="request_type" value="strategy" />

          <label>
            Full name
            <input type="text" name="full_name" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Email
            <input type="email" name="email" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Country of residence
            <input type="text" name="country" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Budget for strategy service (EUR equivalent)
            <input type="number" name="budget" min="1" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Your main goal
            <textarea name="goal" rows="3"></textarea>
          </label>

          <label>
            What can you invest in? (cash, crypto, stocks, etc.)
            <textarea name="assets" rows="2"></textarea>
          </label>

          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Submit strategy request</button>

          <p class="card-note">
            Any strategy ideas are not a promise of returns. Markets and people can
            change, and you can lose money.
          </p>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTACT -->
    <section id="contact" class="section section-alt">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Contact AmicBridge</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">
          If you have questions about how the private network works, the identity
          checks, or the role of AmicBridge as a trusted bridge, you can contact the
          founder directly or use this form.
        </p>

        <form
          class="form"
          action="https://formspree.io/f/movgnjyd"
          method="POST"
        >
          <input
            type="hidden"
            name="_subject"
            value="New CONTACT message from AmicBridge"
          />
          <input type="hidden" name="request_type" value="contact" />

          <label>
            Your name
            <input type="text" name="name" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Your email
            <input type="email" name="email" required />
          </label>

          <label>
            Message
            <textarea name="message" rows="4"></textarea>
          </label>

          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-full">Send message</button>

          <p class="card-note">
            For security, do not send passwords, card details or private keys in this
            form.
          </p>
        </form>

        <div class="contact-card" style="margin-top:1.5rem;">
          <p><strong>CEO:</strong> Robert</p>
          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong>
            <a href="mailto:Robertamicolsen@gmail.com">Robertamicolsen@gmail.com</a>
          </p>
          <p class="card-note">
            Direct email is available for important questions and partnership discussions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <p class="footer-main">
          AmicBridge is a private, Cyprus-based peer-to-peer network that collects
          structured borrowing, lending and investment strategy requests from
          identity-checked members. It does not hold user funds, handle money or
          crypto, act as a bank or financial advisor, or guarantee any approvals,
          matches, results or repayments. Members remain fully responsible for their
          decisions, agreements and legal obligations.
        </p>
        <p class="footer-meta">
          © {year} AmicBridge · A private, trusted bridge between people.
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>

  <style>
    :global(body) {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #f8f9fc;
      color: #1e1e1e;
    }
    .page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .section {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }
    .section-alt {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-block: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .section-lead {
      max-width: 50rem;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .header {
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
    }
    .header-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }
    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #111;
    }
    .logo-mark {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #3b82f6, #6366f1);
      color: white;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .logo-text {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .nav-link {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #444;
      padding-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .nav-link:hover {
      color: #000;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
      background: #fafbfe;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .hero-inner {
      max-width: 830px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.1rem;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.03rem;
      color: #4b5563;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    }
    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .hero-note {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #666;
      max-width: 32rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .btn {
      border-radius: 0.45rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: 0.18s;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #6366f1, #3b82f6);
      color: white;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4f46e5, #2563eb);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      border-color: #d0d3da;
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #222;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f1f2f5;
      border-color: #babec7;
    }
    .btn-full {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 0.6rem;
    }

    .how-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1.2rem;
    }
    .how-step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .how-number {
      width: 26px;
      height: 26px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #eef0ff;
      border: 1px solid #c7ccf7;
      color: #3f4cd0;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
    }

    .principles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    .principle-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e4e6eb;
      border-radius: 0.8rem;
      padding: 1.2rem 1rem;
    }

    .bridge-list li {
      margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
      color: #3b3b3b;
    }

    .form {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.8rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 0.9rem;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #555;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.4rem;
    }
    input,
    select,
    textarea {
      border-radius: 0.4rem;
      border: 1px solid #d2d5dc;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 0.55rem 0.7rem;
      font: inherit;
      outline: none;
    }
    input:focus,
    select:focus,
    textarea:focus {
      border-color: #6366f1;
    }
    .form-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }
    .card-note {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .contact-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 0.8rem;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      max-width: 420px;
    }
    .contact-card a {
      color: #4755f1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: #505050;
    }
    .footer-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .footer-main {
      max-width: 40rem;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .principles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
      .how-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .form,
      .contact-card {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</html>
